Package cz.vse.java.connections.clientSide

Class C2RConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.vse.java.connections.utils.management.AConnectionWithRouter
      • cz.vse.java.connections.clientSide.C2RConnection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConnection, ICSConnection, IProblemSolver, ISubject, java.lang.Runnable
    public class C2RConnection
extends AConnectionWithRouter
implements ICSConnection, ISubject

    The class of C2RConnection is used to abstractly define the type of the instances.

    Child of AConnectionWithRouter abstract instance used for establishing communication with Router side connection (R2CConnection on the other side).

    It's implementing interfaces of ISubject and ICSConnection.

    Written for project "Connections2".
    Version:
    02. 04. 2020 .vse.java.connections
    Author:
    Vojtěch Pavlů
